{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"06561d803d1c5f7d0dede4ce34564e9b","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe path when a `.jsonl` file is deleted before `claude_consult`:\n\n---\n\n**1. `consultService.consult()`** (`src/consult.ts:52`) — acquires `cost:` lock, calls `resolveRoute()`\n\n**2. `resolveRoute()`** (`src/consult.ts:249`) — two cases:\n\n**If `session_id` explicitly provided:**\n- Session found in SQLite; project mismatch checked (`src/consult.ts:251-257`)\n- `sessionFileExists(claude_session_id)` called (`src/claude.ts:104-122`) — searches `~/.claude/sessions/{id}.json`, `sessions/{id}.jsonl`, and deep-scan in `~/.claude/projects`\n- **File missing** → `db.markSessionOrphaned(session.id)` (`src/db.ts:518-530`): status set to `orphaned`, `orphan_recovery` event logged\n- Returns `RouteResolution` with `selectedSession = null`, `bootstrapContext = buildBootstrapContext(oldView, \"orphaned\")`, `wasOrphanRecovery = true`\n\n**If `session_id` null (auto-route):**\n- `listMatchCandidates` skips orphaned sessions silently\n- `sessionFileExists` checked on each candidate before considering reuse (`src/consult.ts:300-301`)\n- Orphaned sessions excluded from scoring\n\n**3. `invokeWithRouteLock()`** (`src/consult.ts:97-115`) — since `selectedSession = null`, skips route lock, goes straight to `invokeClaude()`\n\n**4. `invokeClaude()`** (`src/consult.ts:117`):\n- Bootstrap context (topic, summary, decisions, files, tags, aliases) injected into prompt via `buildSessionContext()` or `buildBootstrapContext()`\n- `claude.runPrompt(prompt)` called **without `--resume`** — new Claude session created\n- New `claude_session_id` returned and stored in SQLite\n- Event `new_session` logged with `was_orphan_recovery = true`\n\n---\n\n**Outcome**: Orphaned session stays in SQLite as historical record; new session created; compact registry context transferred so no architectural memory is lost. The `was_orphan_recovery = true` flag in `session_events` provides full observability for the routing decision."}],"model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":129206,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0},"service_tier":"standard","context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1bc568d1-5a5f-4314-b4be-00aca006f5e1","uuid":"6112572e-db2b-4187-961e-522ff98ff570"}
